dataIdInfo.idAbs: This polygon data layer represents land use for Outagamie County, Wisconsin in 2010. It is a feature class within the geodatabase Outagamie_LandUse_2010.gdb.[Land use data for Outagamie County]
dataIdInfo.idPurp:
This layer is intended for reference and mapping purposes, and may be used for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data.
[The data are created to serve as base information for use in GIS systems for a variety of planning and analysis purposes. Use of data for Engineering work is prohibited.]
dataIdInfo.suppInfo: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements. For complete metadata documentation, please visit http://data-ocgis.opendata.arcgis.com/ .
